.TH I2CD 8 "@HIDLOOM_VERSION@" "HIDloom" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
i2cd \- OLED and status display daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B python3 -m i2cd.i2cd
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B i2cd
renders boot, daemon status, output mode, layer, warning, and direct-frame FPS
status to the OLED display. It also exposes an event socket for short alerts.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B -h, --help
Show command help.
.SH FILES
.TP
.B /usr/lib/hidloom/config/default/i2cd.json
Packaged default configuration.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR hidloom-oled (1),
.BR hidloom-notify (1),
.BR logicd (8)
.br
Display documentation:
https://github.com/cqa02303/hidloom/tree/@HIDLOOM_GIT_SHA@/docs/daemon
